'''大衛·密斯凱維吉'''({{lang-en|David Miscavige}}, {{IPAc-en|ˌ|m|ɪ|s|ˈ|k|æ|v|ə|dʒ}}；{{bd|1960年|4月30日||}})，目前是[[山達基教會|山達基教會]]的領導人<ref>{{cite web|title=Official Church of Scientology: David Miscavige, Religious Technology Center Chairman of the Board|url=http://www.scientology.org/david-miscavige.html|work=Scientology.org|accessdate=November 6, 2013|archive-date=2012-11-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121103132624/http://www.scientology.org/david-miscavige.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他的正式頭銜是{{tsl|en|Religious Technology Center|宗教技術中心}}(RTC)的[[董事會主席|董事會主席]]，是控制控制''Scientology''商標的一間美商公司，擁有[[戴尼提|戴尼提]]與[[山達基|山達基]]的商標權與版權。

當大衛·密斯凱維吉還是青少年的時候，原本作為教會創辦人[[L·罗恩·贺伯特|L·罗恩·贺伯特]]的一位副手 (a "[[Commodore's_Messenger_Organization|Commodore's messenger]]")。在1980年代初期，他被提升到一個領導職；且在1987年，成為宗教技術中心的董事會主席<ref>{{cite journal| last = Young | first = Robert Vaughn| title =Scientology from inside out | journal =Quill magazine |volume=81|issue=9 | date =November–December 1993 }}</ref>。

山達基教會的官方傳記描述大衛·密斯凱維吉是“山達基教的宗教領袖”<ref name="christensen">{{Cite book| last = Christensen | first = Dorthe Refund |chapter= Inventing L. Ron Hubbard | editor= James R. Lewis (scholar) | title = Controversial New Religions | publisher = [[Oxford_University_Press|Oxford University Press]] | year = 2004 | isbn = 0-19-515683-8 |page= 247}}</ref><ref name="Behar">{{cite news | last =Behar | first =Richard | authorlink =Richard Behar | title =The Thriving Cult of Greed and Power | work =[[Time_(magazine)|Time]] | publisher =Time Inc. | date =May 6, 1991 | url =http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,972865,00.html | accessdate =October 12, 2010 | archive-date =2012-05-24 | archive-url =https://archive.today/20120524/http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,972865,00.html | dead-url =yes }}</ref><ref name="zellner">{{Cite book| last =Zellner|first=William W.|author2=Richard T. Schaefer |chapter= David Miscavige | editor= William W. Zellner | title = Extraordinary Groups: An Examination of Unconventional Lifestyles | publisher = Worth Publishers|edition=8th| year = 2007 | isbn = 0-7167-7034-2 | pages= 285–286}}</ref>。

== 生平 ==
1960年，大衛·密斯凱維吉(以下簡稱大衛)出生於美國[[賓夕法尼亞州|賓夕法尼亞州]][[費城|費城]][[巴克斯縣|巴克斯縣]]<ref name=philly>{{cite news | first = J. | last = Nark | url = http://articles.philly.com/2012-01-03/news/30583520_1_david-miscavige-scientology-lrh | title = From here to Scientology: Worldwide leader David Miscavige's Philly-area roots | date = January 3, 2012 | work = McClatchy - Tribune Business News | accessdate = September 16, 2013 | archive-date = 2016-04-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160410093048/http://articles.philly.com/2012-01-03/news/30583520_1_david-miscavige-scientology-lrh | dead-url = no }}</ref>的一個信仰[[天主教會|羅馬天主教]]的波蘭與意大利裔的混合家庭，父親是Ron Miscavige、母親是Loretta Miscavige<ref name="TMBS">{{cite web| url=http://www.sptimes.com/TampaBay/102598/scientologypart2.html| title=The man behind Scientology, part 2| accessdate=August 27, 2007| author=Thomas C. Tobin| date=October 25, 1998| work=[[St._Petersburg_Times|St. Petersburg Times]]| archive-date=2006-06-18| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060618092857/http://www.sptimes.com/TampaBay/102598/scientologypart2.html| dead-url=no}}</ref>，他是家中四個孩子最年輕的一個。大衛在[[新澤西州|新澤西州]]的[[Willingboro_Township,_New_Jersey|Willingboro鎮]]當地成長<ref>Nark, Jason. [http://articles.philly.com/2012-01-03/news/30583520_1_david-miscavige-scientology-lrh "From here to Scientology: Worldwide leader David Miscavige's Philly-area roots"] {{Wayback|url=http://articles.philly.com/2012-01-03/news/30583520_1_david-miscavige-scientology-lrh |date=20160410093048 }}, ''[[The_Philadelphia_Inquirer|The Philadelphia Inquirer]]'', January 3, 2012. Accessed April 9, 2013. "Miscavige's middle-class Catholic upbringing in Willingboro, N.J., abruptly changed four decades ago when his childhood asthma led the family to another utopian vision - that of L. Ron Hubbard."</ref>，高中時，他就讀了Marple新城高中。孩童時期，他有[[哮喘|哮喘]]與[[過敏|過敏]]等症狀的困擾，當時他玩[[棒球|棒球]]跟[[美式足球|美式足球]]。

他的父親是一位吹[[小號|小號]]的玩家，對[[山達基|山達基]]感到興趣，他帶了大衛一起去見一位山達基的聽析師。據父子倆的敘述，一個45分鐘[[戴尼提|戴尼提]]會議治愈了大衛的疾病。

大衛的家庭在1971年加入[[山達基|山達基]]，並最終轉移到[[山達基教會|山達基教會]]在[[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[Saint_Hill_Manor|Saint Hill Manor]]的全球總部。大衛在十二歲的時候，他被進行了山達基[[Auditing_(Scientology)|auditing sessions]]的聽析計劃。家庭回到費城的幾年內，大衛就在英國讀了一間[[Saint_Hill_Manor|Saint Hill Manor]]當地的[[高中|高中]]，然而大衛被山達基較為認為是"12歲的神童"，就成為該教會史上最年輕的山達基聽析師<ref>{{cite web |url=http://articles.philly.com/2012-01-03/news/30583520_1_david-miscavige-scientology-lrh |title=From here to Scientology: Worldwide leader David Miscavige's Philly-area roots |last=Nark |first=Jason |accessdate=2015-11-23 |archive-date=2016-04-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160410093048/http://articles.philly.com/2012-01-03/news/30583520_1_david-miscavige-scientology-lrh |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

1976年，在大衛16歲的生日，他離開高中與他的父親的同意搬到美國佛羅里達州的清水市，並加入了一個組織，那就是[[海洋機構_(山達基)|海洋機構]]。他在海洋機構中早期的工作是包括幫忙發送電報、地面照護(grounds-keeping)、食物服務(food service)、以及拍攝山達基宣傳手冊的照片。

大衛然後加入了一組名為 [[Commodore's_Messenger_Organization|Commodore's Messenger Organization]] (CMO)的年輕山達基人小組。該小組原本是幫教主[[L·羅恩·賀伯特|L·羅恩·賀伯特]]跑腿，但隨著他們長大進入青春期，賀伯特強化了他們的影響力<ref>Sappell, J., & Welkos, R. W. (June 24, 1990). The man in control series: The scientology story. today: The making of L. ron hubbard. first in a six-part series.NEXT: Part two-- the selling of scientology. Los Angeles Times (Pre-1997 Fulltext)</ref>。

1986年在賀伯特死後，大衛·密斯凱維吉在日後的權力鬥爭中擊敗賀伯特的第三任妻子，大衛成為教會的新任主席。

